Sentencas: Porous substrates of La0.7Sr0.3MnO3 were prepared by heating the mixtures of La0.7Sr0.3MnO3 and corn-starch.
Titulo: POROUS CATHODE SUBSTRATES OF LA0.7SR0.3MNO3 FOR SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELLS

Sentencas: The electrical conductivity, 3-point bending strength, porosity, and air permeability were examined as a function of the corn-starch content and the heating conditions.
Titulo: POROUS CATHODE SUBSTRATES OF LA0.7SR0.3MNO3 FOR SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELLS

Sentencas: These physical properties strongly depended on the content of corn-starch.
Titulo: POROUS CATHODE SUBSTRATES OF LA0.7SR0.3MNO3 FOR SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELLS

Sentencas: The porous substrates with high air permeability of 5x10(-3)cm4/gs, high bending strength of 30MPa, and high conductivity of 60 S/cm at 1000-degrees-C were prepared by controlling the corn-starch content.
Titulo: POROUS CATHODE SUBSTRATES OF LA0.7SR0.3MNO3 FOR SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELLS

Sentencas: The porous substrates are attractive as the cathode for the cathode self-supported solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: POROUS CATHODE SUBSTRATES OF LA0.7SR0.3MNO3 FOR SOLID OXIDE FUEL-CELLS
